      "kind": "round-trip",
      "description": "copy-down on a formula source fills to the adjacent (left) column's data extent, incrementing relative ROW references per copied row: C2 (=B2*10) fills C3/C4 as =B3*10/=B4*10, computing 10/20/30 against B=1/2/3; the C4 formula text confirms the rewrite.",
